  "remarks": "Member of Taliban Supreme Council and advisor to Mullah Mohammed Omar\n(TAi.004) as at June 2010. Leads a Taliban \"front\" (mahaz) as of mid-2013. Believed to\nbe in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Sadat ethnic group. Review pursuant\nto Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 23 Jul. 2010. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
